Ah, 2011 jokes us non KSP-Boomers don't get...

1 hour ago, Second Hand Rocket Science said:

:hailprobe:

Ah, 2011 jokes us non KSP-Boomers don't get...

Joke?

God save our gracious Probe,
Long live our noble Probe,
God save the Probe!
Send it victorious,
Happy and glorious,
Long to reign over us,
God save the Probe!

O Explorer the probe                                                              Destroy our enemies
And make them fall!
Confound their politics,
Frustrate their knavish tricks,
On Thee our hopes we fix,
Probe save us all!
